<h1 class='s-mega'>Hello, I&#8217;m Shay</h1>
<h2>I&#8217;m a product leader with a design and engineering background.</h2>
<p class='s-echo mb-xx-large'>My love is for solving problems. Specifically providing simple solutions to what was previously arcane or impossible. Solutions that, while intuitive, provide value to the customer and business alike.</p>
